data.description: Clay Chalkville Schools!  Quiet Neighborhood!  This Home has all the room you would need for a growing family!  Huge yard for family outside games and get togethers.  Big deck on the back so you can cheer on your favorite team or listen to birds while you drink your glass of tea or cup of coffee.  You can also sit on the front porch and relax, while enjoying the swing.  The Home has a Man Cave or extra Den in Basement to give extra space for the family.  Both HVAC Units are 2-3 years old.  Washer & Dryer, Island in Kitchen, Floor & Wall Cabinets in Master Bath and Storage Building in backyard remain.  Come and make this Home Yours!
